  <h2>When NOT to Minify</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Development:</strong> Keep source files readable during development; only minify for production</li>
    <li><strong>Debugging:</strong> Use source maps to map minified CSS back to original source</li>
    <li><strong>Tiny files:</strong> Files under 1KB see negligible benefit from minification</li>
  </ul>

